        {
            "title": "中國出口衝擊恐帶來生存威脅 歐盟醞釀調整對華貿易政策",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 中國出口的一派繁榮景象，正使其與歐洲貿易關係面臨一觸即發的對抗。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國總統馬克龍稱歐中貿易失衡「令人無法容忍」，並表示當前問題關乎歐洲工業的生死存亡。」 歐盟委員會主席烏爾蘇拉·馮德萊恩認為，歐盟與中國的關係「已到達拐點」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國近期公佈的進出口數據顯示，2025年以來中國對歐盟的貿易順差擴大至接近3000億美元，勢將創歷史新高，這更加凸顯中歐貿易失衡的規模。由於中國賣家將面臨美國關稅的商品轉向歐盟，中國對歐盟的出口額現在是其進口額的兩倍多。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3992dc88-9b05-36b7-9ed5-058602998b1a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rmmXYCefBl27eHiOHtSzEQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8badd73086d30bc54e52a6b21e8f7749\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲對外關係委員會亞洲項目主任Andrew Small表示：「歐洲正在真正感受到中國衝擊波的威力。過去幾個月來各方出現更大緊迫感，雖然相關情況並未全部公開，但確已召開多場危機應對會議。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">曾擔任馮德萊恩中國問題顧問的Small稱，這可能促使歐盟對中國政策進行至少十年來最大規模的反思。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">多年來，歐盟一直因烏克蘭戰爭以及近期美國總統特朗普關稅政策而分心，如今終於聚焦在中國身上，準備出台Small所稱的「積壓已久」的一系列措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Forces Reckoning in Europe as Trade Boom Turns Existential</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Ran Li、Alexander Weber、Andrew Langley.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E6%81%90%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E9%86%9E%E9%87%80%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96-031801849.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-12 14:15:45",
