            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "彭博新聞午間分享 你會想知道的五件事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">適度刺激</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中央經濟工作會議官方通稿周四晚間發布，示意明年將繼續支持經濟，但刺激力度將適度。11月一系列關鍵經濟數據將於下周發布，經濟學家預計將會再度顯示成長乏力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">化解困局</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萬科債務危機急轉直下，深鐵放棄輸血成致命一擊，引發連鎖反應並最終迫使該公司申請延期償還部分債務。萬科據悉尋求將第二支境內債展期一年。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">晶片競爭</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普簽署一項旨在限制州級部門對AI行業監管的命令，他表示此舉對於支持新興技術、應對各州監管政策的差異至關重要，業界擔心這種差異會阻礙行業發展。此外，研究公司TechInsights的報告發現華為和中芯國際在晶片生產技術領域取得進展。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-be08c566-3d33-3949-aaa6-29e6df85a6ac-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">俄烏局勢</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">面對美國加大力度施壓基輔接受和平方案，烏克蘭總統澤連斯基拋出通過公投來決定頓巴斯命運的想法。另據悉歐盟將於周五批准一項協議，動用緊急權力延長對俄羅斯資產的凍結。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">亞洲動態</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在聯合政府中的主要政黨人民黨威脅要撤回支持之後，泰國總理阿努廷解散國會下院，為提前舉行大選鋪平道路。根據泰國法律，下議院解散後45至60天內必須舉行選舉。美印方面，莫迪稱與川普進行了友好熱情的通話，雙方談判人員仍在致力於化解貿易協議中的分歧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%8D%88%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B-041531552.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-12 12:55:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "博通在盤後交易中下挫 對AI銷售額展望未能達到投資者的高期望值",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"博通在盤後交易中下挫 對AI銷售額展望未能達到投資者的高期望值\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"677\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2LLj0aDHkVaBVFHCQFmVDQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY3NztjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-12/ab8eff90-bc91-11ef-b6d7-f7a87cfc1131\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">博通在盤後交易中下挫 對AI銷售額展望未能達到投資者的高期望值</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
